{"tid":856804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 自重啦","createTime":"2018-10-10T19:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T07:15:52.000Z","uid":54293,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d71def83af53db562f30958dfa0184095c5218d1","tid":856804,"uid":54293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:16:26.000Z","msg":"住hall 俾人偷嘢食偷得多<br />\n所以自己買咗個箱鑽窿塔把鎖上去<br />\n點知頭先一開雪櫃<br />\n見到咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咁撚desperate 要爆我鎖去偷嘢食呀<br />\n不過佢都係白廢心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為個箱入面得三個蘋果<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪好撚失望呢 爆我鎖嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝所有住hall偷人嘢食嘅人<br />\n百病纏身 長命百歲"},{"pid":"f5929